–	*Nicholas R. Lardy, “The Role of Foreign Trade and Investment in China’s Economic Transformation,” in Ross Garnaut and Yiping Huang (eds.), Growth Without Miracles: Readings on the Chinese Economy in the Era of Reform (New York: Oxford University Press, 2001).
–	*Susan H. Whiting, Power and Wealth in Rural China: The Political Economy of Institutional Change (New York: Cambridge University Press, 2001), Chapter 4.
–	關志雄、童振源主編，人民幣匯率 : 經濟與戰略分析 （臺北：兩岸遠景交流基金會，2004）。
–	Yasheng Huang and Tarun Khanna, “Indigenous versus Foreign Business Models,” in Edward Friedman and Bruce Gilley (eds.), Asia’s Giants: Comparing China and India (New York: Palgrave Macmillan, 2005), pp. 161-182.
