–	Jean Oi, “Old Problems for New Leaders: Institutional Disjunctures in Rural China,” in Yun-han Chu, Chih-cheng Lo and Ramon Myers (eds.), The New Chinese Leadership: Challenges and Opportunities after the 16th Party Congress (Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 2004).
–	*何增科、高新軍、楊雪冬、賴海榕，基層民主和地方治理創新（北京：中央編譯出版社，2004），第一～八章。
